{"tid":2442200,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"地署測量員示威攜鐳射筆 判監3個月","createTime":"2021-03-11T08:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T11:19:35.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6486b59e34e57c5886f011034a526ed9a7a545b3","tid":2442200,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"一名地政總署測量員在前年10月的示威被警方拘捕，身上藏有一支雷射筆，被控管有攻擊性武器罪，在觀塘裁判法院被判監3個月。裁判官屈麗雯表示，感到被告無悔意，無任何減刑理由，而被告管有的雷射筆屬3B級別，可發出能量強光，可傷害人的眼晴，加上案發時現場有堵路情況，考慮所有因素後決定判監。辯方表示會提出上訴，被告獲准保釋。 33歲被告雷启添，案發日在牛頭角遊樂場附近，在無合法權限或辯解，而攜有一支雷射筆。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2382546&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHcwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=0557d5c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382546</a>"},{"pid":"2e3fa10995d3884e08c5dbd8194b370eff439f68","tid":2442200,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"強姦無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846359aa23eea258d8fa77796c3db923562119e9","tid":2442200,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e3fa10995d3884e08c5dbd8194b370eff439f68","tid":2442200,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"強姦無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:16:05.000Z","msg":"🤫🤫楊明都係啦"},{"pid":"d61e1c5c12c85212458329937e66bb119d4884f8","tid":2442200,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:18:42.000Z","msg":"連測量員都唔可以有laser pen<br />\n有咩人有資格有laser pen<br />\n<br />\nd狗就大條道理攞白光laser 射人隻眼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a140be28c998257e2f4f3e16b533eb21b12cfa83","tid":2442200,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:3